hopobject.body: How much will it cost to send this letter to ? ab doer twist abdoer 360 The city's current ban on NYPD profiling covers race, ethnicity, religion and national origin. The racial profiling bill expands the categories to age, gender, gender identity or expressions, sexual orientation, immigration status, disability and housing status. The bill also allows the plaintiffs to bring lawsuits alleging racial profiling to state court.
